{"tid":2391283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK Jennie擔任知名燒酒品牌代言人","createTime":"2021-02-02T06:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T10:48:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":18,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f6fc1fed532e9b9641cae813155099c841994079","tid":2391283,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:14:33.000Z","msg":"樂天七星飲料今日宣佈，旗下燒酒品牌「初飲初樂」選擇女團BLACKPINK成員Jennie擔任最新代言人，再次證實了她與眾不同的人氣~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_39d03d63d390f24c02d84652e6d96c6e/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-02/133433-895695.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_39d03d63d390f24c02d84652e6d96c6e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-02%2F133433-895695.jpeg&h=07b53322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖：樂天七星飲料）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJennie去年在女團個人品牌評價里多次佔據第一，這個月還開通了自己的Youtube頻道，目前只上傳了一條影片，觀看次數超過2400萬，而頻道訂閱人數更已經接近500萬！足以見得她在全球範圍的受歡迎程度：<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b219fdad02900c7c630f8bff5e446e75/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-02/133433-895696.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b219fdad02900c7c630f8bff5e446e75%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-02%2F133433-895696.png&h=4765752d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖：Youtube）<br />\n<br />\n同時，「燒酒廣告模特」也一直是業界內衡量人氣高低的重要標準，也可以說是判斷「大勢藝人」與否的尺規，之前為初飲初樂擔任代言的藝人有李孝利、新慜娥、秀智等等，咖位程度可見一斑~<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/firstsoju/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ffirstsoju%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=b98bd218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/firstsoju/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n據悉，Jennie為初飲初樂拍攝的廣告很快就會公開了，讓人好期待啊！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kxjen01?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1356454680977620993%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F133433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkxjen01%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1356454680977620993%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.koreastardaily.com%252Ftc%252Fnews%252F133433&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=c073194f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kxjen01?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1356454680977620993%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F133433</a>"},{"pid":"d8959a0f2fa9afe8a5e0f0b1728db952d00e4b00","tid":2391283,"uid":255310,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"勁正..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c629f69d21c5daf1069c45a6882e0a0aa2e238","tid":2391283,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8959a0f2fa9afe8a5e0f0b1728db952d00e4b00","tid":2391283,"uid":255310,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"勁正..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"唔飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d13eaa15717fb19ee599a2f333f6dc7b67822d","tid":2391283,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:22:35.000Z","msg":"其實咩味韓國燒酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲完可唔可以上佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3147709bc9357dfda989f1f70acb2e56833c22","tid":2391283,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike"